This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with the analysis of argumentative relations between text units. It also involves the use of machine learning algorithms to classify these relations, which falls under the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of context in argument analysis, which could be relevant to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-categories.
